com.teamonehundred.pixelboat.ui

Class Button

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamonehundred.pixelboat.ui.UIElement
      • com.teamonehundred.pixelboat.ui.Button
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Switch

    public abstract class Button
extends UIElement
    A basic UI button class with three states - normal, hovered, and pressed Its callbacks can be overridden to implement custom behaviours
